* Type Validation\nConstraints
** CHECK Constraints
***_ Custom validation rules
***_ Enforced on insert/update
***_ ALTER TABLE ADD CONSTRAINT
** Pattern Matching
***_ REGEXP for format checks
***_ Validate numeric strings
***_ Email/phone formats
** Date Validation
***_ try_cast() in constraint
***_ Rejects invalid date strings
***_ Event date validation
** Important
***_ Existing rows validated on ALTER
***_ Plan for large table migrations
***_ Constraint can be dropped if needed
@endmindmap
